Lunarpine returned to the Ark after mourning the destruction of 
Shadow Wings frame. he knew his body couldn't power two sparks for 
very long, he knew he had to act. he went to a transport pod and set 
a course for the Cybertronian Fire. he knew that he might be able to 
use the computer there to find a solution.
